snippet.title: Bound High (Nintendo Virtual Boy) Complete Playthrough
snippet.description: This is a complete playthrough for the main mode on Bound High for the Virtual Boy. Bound High was completed, but actually never released to the public and sold at stores.  Nintendo canned the Virtual Boy before it was released. This game was leaked many years later. The game itself has a main adventure, and there are a few  of "mini games" on it as well, perhaps I will play those in a different video. This video is a playthrough of the main adventure, called "Adventure of Chalvo", and is played on medium difficulty.
